\nbetween the dressed expressions and quantum expectations, even at the late\ntime. Thus, the dressed metric approach captures the essence of the full\nquantum treatment for the dust dominated case, whereas it is bound to receive\nsignificant correction for the dark energy dominated universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 17:55:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
