g-data multitaper version of complex demodulation, which extracts the\nlow-frequency envelope from a modulated signal. We argue that multitaper power\nspectrum estimators should be used for all time series with regular observing\ncadence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 19:19:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-01"}
