atter type of variations results in appreciable changes in the precipitation\nL-shell profiles and can significantly modify the net electron losses during\nsuccessive tracks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 20:31:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
