rgeometric-type functions. Besides identifying the characteristic\nfunctions, we also manage to characterize the pair of the corresponding van\nDantzig random variables revealing that one of them is infinitely divisible.\nFinally, we investigate the possibility that the Riemann $\\xi$ function belongs\nto this class.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2022 02:00:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-01"}
